\begin_layout Standard
Within this broad landscape,
 Differential Evolution (DE) has become one of the most influential frameworks for real-parameter optimization 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Storn"
literal "false"

\end_inset

,
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
