\end_inset

.
 Its compact algorithmic structure can induce markedly different search behaviors through the choice of mutation base vector,
 difference scheme,
 and crossover operator.
 Classical strategies range from the exploratory DE/rand/1/bin,
 which uses a randomly selected base vector and promotes diversity,
 to the exploitative DE/best/1/bin,
 which perturbs the incumbent solution and accelerates local convergence at the risk of premature convergence 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
